    <div class="about__bio">
      <p>
        WRONGORIGIN is an audiovisual entity concerned with in-between spaces— occurences that should have taken 	place in your american dream—
        the hours, places, and moments that exist at the edges of the world. Frames taken in places that toll 	roads and fossil fuel industry monopolized high-ways won't take you. Decentralized snippets of realities 	other than those found at the starting point.
        Current works span documentaries, architecture, and portraiture.
      </p>
      <p>
        Based between DFW and wherever the next shot is taken. Available for 
        editorial, commercial, and personal projects.
